title: Day by Day Organizer PRO
description:
Day by Day is a planning application designed to fully implement Google Calendar and Google Tasks as all-in-one Android application. With its help you can plan your future schedule using any Android device and this schedule will be available for all your phones and tablets connected to Internet.

WHAT'S NEW

* Persian localizations was added. Other localizations were improved (thanks to our translators!)
* Now you can add your contacts to tasks (only PRO and paid versions)
* Other changes
* Bug fixes
